Class LayerDescriptor

java.lang.Object
  mapnik.LayerDescriptor

public class LayerDescriptor
extends java.lang.Object

Read-only access to a mapnik::layer_descriptor on a Datasource. As a value type, this class has Java fields that mirror the native fields.
